title: H.O.U.S.E.
subtitle: Open User-Friendly Search Engine  --  created by GeoJEM

about.aboutContent:
An open and user-friendly search engine to connect tenants and renters with important housing resources from the City of Toronto. To connect and support vulnerable communities with the power to access stable housing, and keep housing proprietors accountable. 


We cannot succeed individually unless everyone succeeds together.

1. Click on any apartment to learn more


2. Search Bar: this tool searches addresses of only those registered with RentSafeTO


3. Layers: there are a number of layers to turn off and on


4. Filter: refine the visible apartments by evaluation score and property owner


5. Statistics: reveals the total apartments registered and total average evaluation score
